subject: Bicycles and Bicycling
Vuelta a Espana (Bicycle Race)
lead_paragraph: Nairo Quintana took the overall lead of the Vuelta a España from his Movistar teammate Alejandro Valverde after a rainy and mountainous ninth stage.
